data.description: Check out this charming brick home located in the desirable Arrowhead community! Conveniently located at the corner of Atlanta Highway and I-85, and just minutes from Eastchase Shopping Center. With 1773 square feet, this 3 bedroom 2 bath spacious house is ready for its new owners! The open floor plan in the dining room and great room is perfect for entertaining. You will love the 14’ ceilings in the great room with beautiful built-in bookcases and fireplace complete with gas logs! This home also features a formal dining room with custom cabinetry. The kitchen offers great counter and cabinet space with tons of natural lighting from the windows. The nice sized laundry room,right off the kitchen, has extra cabinets for storage and a built in desk area. The spacious master bedroom is accompanied with a full size bathroom, garden tub, and a walk in closet! Two additional bedrooms that share a full bath will complete the inside of the house! Beautiful crown moulding and plantation shutters throughout! The home offers two attics for plenty of storage, one in the hallway and one above the garage. Out back you will find a 2 car garage with an extra storage room inside. Lastly, the cozy little patio makes for a relaxing grilling area to entertain! Nestled on a quiet street right off the golf course just a few blocks away from the Arrowhead Country Club. The new air conditioner unit was put in last summer. And the entire attic was sprayed with foam insulation as well. Come see it for yourself!
